# REVIEW FINDINGS

## Finding 1 — CRITICAL: no-op-reset
File: src/gateway/rate-limiter.ts:42
Message: Counter is never decremented — window reset is a no-op

## Finding 2 — ERROR: non-atomic-increment
File: src/gateway/rate-limiter.ts:67
Message: Race condition: counter increment is not atomic

